{
  "stem": "7832.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He's not going to be here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tortured him and his family, and they shot him in the middle of the square.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tortured his two daughters to death and he watched.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they shot the rest of the family in the square of the city, and then-- because he was one of the people that picked up the bodies and buried them at the cemetery before they took him away.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came into the ghetto, and when he saw my father, and he knew my father was waiting for them to come into the ghetto so we can go together, he says-- he told him what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know what happened to my other-- to my father's other cousin, whether they-- they came into the ghetto and went to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I never saw them again either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in Munkacs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and so we went on the train and we started on our journey-- thinking that we're going to Tokaj.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a couple of days, my father-- we were in closed wagons, but the only thing-- the outside-- we had a crack in the-- in the wall on the wagon, so somebody was able to-- at the time to look outside and-- and maybe see a glimpse of something that they can recognize.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a couple of days later, my father said we are not going to Tokaj.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just left our borders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are out of the country and we are heading towards Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See, he recognized the route.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so everybody started to remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now all the adults were like very, very upset in the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, the train was so packed we had no room to move around.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
